---
---

<section class="support section" id="support">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">支持我</h2>
    <div class="support-content">
      <p>如果你觉得我的内容有价值，可以请我喝杯咖啡 ☕</p>
      <div class="support-qr">
        <div class="qr-placeholder">
          <span>打赏二维码</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .support-content {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .support-content p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .support-qr {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .qr-placeholder {
    width: 160px;
    height: 160px;
    border: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }
</style>
